Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:08.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,472)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.54,0:01:06.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:06.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.06,0:01:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村最顶级的日间餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's premiere daytime eatery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:12.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(674,842)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.33,0:01:11.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关门时间差不多就
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where it'll be closing time right
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.67,0:01:12.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:12.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:14.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(342,918)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.53,0:01:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八点了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,8:00
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.56,0:01:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永别了  傻蛋们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, suckers
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.24,0:01:19.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟个小姐有一场热辣约会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:19.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a hot date with a little lady
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这小姐就叫做竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and her name is Clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.93,0:01:23.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:23.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.63,0:01:24.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们还开门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:24.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you open?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看牌子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Read the sign
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.81,0:01:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要份豪华蟹黄堡还有双倍辣海草条
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have a Krabby Patty Deluxe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a double chili kelp fries
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.48,0:01:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you won't
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不能一整晚都待这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hang out here all night
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.98,0:01:35.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有好日子要过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:35.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l've got a life
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.36,0:01:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不要我钱就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, fine, if you don't want my money
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.70,0:01:42.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你意思是  要是我们等会还营业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:42.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean, if we stayed open later
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.54,0:01:43.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就会给我们钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:43.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'd give us your money?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.83,0:01:44.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:44.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.08,0:01:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生  欢迎来到夜班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward, welcome to the night shift
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:46.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,606)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.71,0:01:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从现在起  蟹堡王每天24小时营业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From now on, The Krusty Krab is open 24 hours a day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.99,0:01:54.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:54.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我们再也不用下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we never have to stop working
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.63,0:02:04.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:04.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.14,0:02:05.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明早见  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:05.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you in the morning, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不能一整晚都待这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hang out here all night
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.99,0:02:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有好日子要过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a life
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不挺好的吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就我跟你几小时几小时几小时在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just you and me together for hours and hours and hours?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后等到出太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then the sun'll come up?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.65,0:02:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是明天了  结果我们还在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it'll be tomorrow, and we'll still be working
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟睡衣派对一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll be just like a sleepover
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.28,0:02:25.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是我们会流满汗沾满油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:25.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only we'll be sweaty and covered with grease
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好摇滚了吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to rock, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.50,0:02:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.47,0:02:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  因为有客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good, 'cause we've got customers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打我打得越用力越好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please hit me as hard as you can
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.09,0:02:37.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:37.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.84,0:02:39.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在厨房里干活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:39.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm working in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.34,0:02:41.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上干的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:41.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At night
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别犹豫  打下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你猜怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, guess what?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.62,0:02:45.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在切生菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:45.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm chopping lettuce
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.91,0:02:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上切的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at night
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.97,0:02:49.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  我在擦厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:49.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at me, I'm swabbing the bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上擦的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at night
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我烫到我手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I burned my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上烫的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At night
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.86,0:03:03.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上  晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:03:03.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Night, night
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.13,0:03:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Night
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我消停一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.67,0:03:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  出去倒垃圾让我安静会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, give me a moment's peace and take out the trash
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.05,0:03:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.72,0:03:13.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去倒垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:13.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Taking out the trash
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at n
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.47,0:03:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要我出去倒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean, outside?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  垃圾桶就在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's where the dumpster is, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l don't know, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面有点黑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's kind of dark out there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为你喜欢夜班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I thought you liked the night shift
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.98,0:03:31.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:31.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.23,0:03:35.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:35.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Piece of cake
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说你不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you're not afraid?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我怕  特别是过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I am, especially after
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.13,0:03:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  你懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.17,0:03:58.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:58.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I know?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处都有报道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all over the news
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  我多半不该说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, I-I probably shouldn't
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.78,0:04:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这夜班会上不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lt would ruin the night shift for you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.14,0:04:15.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你从来就没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:15.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean you've never heard the story of the
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.98,0:04:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲子杀人魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Hash-Slinging Slasher"?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伞子扒人摸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Slash-Bringing Hasher?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.11,0:04:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲子杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Hash-slinging Slasher
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懒子拉人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Sash-Wringing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毯子撒人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Trash-Singing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.07,0:04:30.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,螨子罚人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mash-Flinging
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,返子傻人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Flash-Springing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wringing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.24,0:04:34.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,侃  侃子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:34.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the-the Crash
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.71,0:04:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dinging
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  铲子杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, the Hash-Slinging Slasher
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.09,0:04:41.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:41.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.71,0:04:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大多数人只管他叫铲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,most people just call him the Ha
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为他们话音未落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because that's all they have time to say
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会被他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before he
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.10,0:04:52.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:52.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gets them
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我讲铲子杀人魔的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me the story
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.27,0:04:59.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好几年以前  就在这家餐厅里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:59.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Years ago, at this very restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.31,0:05:04.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲子杀人魔曾经也是个煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:04.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Hash-Slinging Slasher used to be a fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.04,0:05:04.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:04.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.99,0:05:05.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:05.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.95,0:05:06.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:06.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过比你笨手笨脚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only clumsier
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后  一天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then one night
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.73,0:05:15.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在切肉饼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:15.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when he was cutting the patties
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.43,0:05:17.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:17.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it happened
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他忘加秘制酱料了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He forgot the secret sauce?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.83,0:05:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没忘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他没有洗手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He didn't wash his hands?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.13,0:05:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有洗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有切整齐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Irregular portions?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.21,0:05:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不小心把自己的手给切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He cut off his own hand by mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean like this?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.09,0:05:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or like this?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or this?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about this?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or this?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正他不是海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Except he wasn't a sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说那手没有再生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So it didn't grow back
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.73,0:05:48.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他用一把生锈铲子接到原先手的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:48.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And he replaced his hand with a rusty spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后  他被公交车给撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then he got hit by a bus
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在他葬礼上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And at his funeral
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they fired him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(742,920)}火 化
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以现在  每逢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So now, every
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.91,0:05:57.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天周几
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:57.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what day is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tuesday
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.11,0:06:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周二晚上  他的冤魂就会回到蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:06:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tuesday night, his ghost returns to The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.70,0:06:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,展开他可怕的复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to wreak his horrible vengeance
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可今晚就是周二晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But tonight's Tuesday night
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那他就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then he'll be coming
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么知道他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How will we know?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有三种迹象会表示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are three signs that signal
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲子杀人魔要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the approach of the Hash-Slinging Slasher
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.31,0:06:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一个迹象  灯会闪来闪去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, the lights will flicker on and off
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位  能来点番茄酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dude, can I have some ketchup?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.28,0:06:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.96,0:06:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二个迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.24,0:06:32.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电话响起来却无人应答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:32.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the phone will ring, and there will be nobody there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后一个迹象  铲子杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And finally, the Hash-Slinging Slasher
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.50,0:06:39.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐着撞了他的公交车的灵魂到了这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:39.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,arrives in the ghost of the bus that ran him over
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后他走下了车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then he exits the bus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.50,0:06:46.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没看两边的车况就过了马路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:46.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and crosses the street without looking both ways
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.17,0:06:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为他早就死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because he's already dead
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.57,0:06:56.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后他会用他的灰白铲子手敲窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:52.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, he taps on the window
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:56.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with his grizzly spatula hand
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他打开门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He opens the door
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He slowly
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,approaches the
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,柜台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,counter
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.11,0:07:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道他接下来会干什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you know what he does next?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.03,0:07:15.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:15.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really want to know?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to know?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他他  他干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, what, what does he do?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.17,0:07:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He gets you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he get
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.81,0:07:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.02,0:07:46.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我就
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:46.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I was
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.23,0:07:48.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:48.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.24,0:07:56.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:56.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I was joking
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.05,0:07:56.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:56.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是假的  没一段真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not true, none of it is true
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没有人会拿铲子当手使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody has a spatula for a hand
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all a joke
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:25.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,332)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:25.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(928,442)}永远营业
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说棒不棒  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lsn't this great, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.62,0:09:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白天从来就没时间擦天花板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's never time to wash the ceiling during the day
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么二十四小时营业
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open 24 hours a day
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全就一馊主意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a stupid idea
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凌晨三点钟谁还想吃什么蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants a Krabby Patty at 3:00 in the morning?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊  凌晨三点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, 3:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒看看这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at this place
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟个鬼地方差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's like a ghost town in here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好玩吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very funny, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.91,0:09:23.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:23.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灯会闪来闪去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"And the lights will flicker on and off"
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟我讲的差不多  我都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like the story, I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.67,0:09:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不动开关是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how are you doing that without moving the switch?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定是蟹堡王的电路太垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must be the stupid faulty wiring in here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建这地方就没考虑要二十四小时营业
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place isn't built to run 24 hours a day
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, what?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太会演了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋就演了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try, what?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.26,0:09:56.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电话铃响起来  却无人应答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:56.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The phone will ring and there will be no one there"
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You crack me up
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  不是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I'm not doing this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要冷静  要冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm down, calm down
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, what was it?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.83,0:10:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There was
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the lights
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the phone
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.71,0:10:14.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墙壁渗出来绿色黏液
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:14.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the walls will ooze green slime
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.73,0:10:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是正常现象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They always do that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三个迹象是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:18.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what was that third thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道公交车这么晚还在开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't know the buses ran this late
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就停了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面有人下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, they're dropping someone off
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伞子拉人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the Sash-Wringing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.03,0:10:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,返子撒人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The-the Flash-Singing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阀子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Fash
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.20,0:10:41.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:41.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,P-Pinging
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲子杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Hash-Slinging Slasher
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At last, you understand
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.78,0:10:48.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:48.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  还没完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am just so touched
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到你历经千辛万苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you would go to the trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打扮成铲子杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to dress up as a ghostly fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站到马路对面去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and stand on the other side of the street
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只为逗我开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just to entertain me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.40,0:11:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定真心喜欢上我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must really like me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.21,0:11:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你的论断有两处问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, there are two problems with your theory
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一  我讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One: I hate you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And two:
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.21,0:11:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都站这了  那家伙怎么会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can that be me, when I'm standing right here?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.36,0:11:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲子杀人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Hash-Slinging Slasher
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.66,0:11:25.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要翻了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:25.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's going to flip me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走开  快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away, get away
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.74,0:11:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  不管我刚才说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, no matter what I've said
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是有点喜欢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've always sort of liked you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.30,0:11:35.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我用你竖笛疏通过我马桶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:35.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I used your clarinet to unclog my toilet
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走开  快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away, get away
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边不欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not welcome here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能申请一份工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have a job application?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把我自个的铲子给带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought my own spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.68,0:11:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先前打过电话  不过因为紧张挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I called earlier, but I hung up 'cause I was nervous
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有推荐信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you have references?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.88,0:11:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  如果打电话和在公交上的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, if that was you on the phone and you on the bus
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那到底是谁在弄灯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then who was flickering the lights?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.58,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(313,351)}蟹老板的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.04\pos(366,536)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:16.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.04\pos(360,550)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.04\pos(412,324)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.04\pos(308,362)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.04\pos(472,688)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:21.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422,488)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一正针两反针
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stitch one, purl two
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that smell?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.85,0:12:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收银机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The register?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四十九块
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forty-nine o
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eight?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少了一分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a penny short
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.61,0:12:38.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:38.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一分钱怎么没了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a penny
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁来帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody, help us
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一分钱而已  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a penny, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.22,0:12:47.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还没什么大不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:47.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.56,0:12:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有钱能使世界转  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's money that makes the world go round, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有钱能使你裤子方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's money that keeps your pants square
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有钱能使章鱼哥用褶边香皂洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's money that keeps Squidward in frilly soap
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丁香味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lilac
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有钱能使我们整修蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's money that paid for all them renovations we did
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七大洋里钱是最重要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing in all the seven seas could matter more
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.85,0:13:06.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重要程度还要大过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:06.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not even that
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.97,0:13:12.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美丽动人的小可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:12.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,scrumptious, curvy cutie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到她了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see her, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加奶酪的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Krabby Patty with cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经典无比
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The classic
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是蟹黄堡  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the sandwich, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是拿着蟹黄堡的那个小可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The curvy cutie holding the sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的驾校教练  泡芙夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my driving teacher, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's married
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她单身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's single
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那她丈夫怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then what happened to Mr. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她不愿意提起这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She doesn't like to talk about it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.29,0:13:40.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿付出一切抱得美人归
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I wouldn't give to have a lass like that on me claw
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.09,0:13:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不我带你过去介绍介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't I take you over and introduce you?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.46,0:13:44.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:44.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我我我太老了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm-I'm too old, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对爱太过古板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too hard-shelled for love
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.66,0:13:50.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且我衣冠也不整
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:50.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, I ain't properly dressed
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come on, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.81,0:13:53.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你挺漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:53.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look great
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.68,0:13:57.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先待在这  我去暖个场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:57.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wait here while I go break the ice
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  等下别去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, no, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.58,0:13:59.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我太紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:13:59.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm too nervous
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快踩刹车  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit the brakes, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.78,0:14:06.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心那棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:06.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch the tree
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.65,0:14:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没在开船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not driving
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没料到会在这看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to see you here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就在这上班  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I work here, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要认识下我老板吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want to meet my boss?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  我没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐好别动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't move
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.34,0:14:24.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  我要向你介绍蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:24.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, I'd like to introduce you to Mr.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  我要向你介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, I'd like to introduce you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老板  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to my boss, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  快问个好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, say hello
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.69,0:14:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说个你好就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just say hello
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或许改天再
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps another time would be
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.99,0:14:47.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:47.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要跟你说句话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's trying to tell you something
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不大懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.87,0:15:02.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板应该说的是他想要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:02.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think Mr. Krabs is saying that he'd like to
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.92,0:15:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用耙子打你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hit you with a rake
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要猜你体重多少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try to guess your weight
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好你这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.34,0:15:12.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:12.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wants to take you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,约个会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on a date
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.24,0:15:24.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真的要带我去约个会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:24.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take me on a date?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I say?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.07,0:15:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得你说话还挺有特色  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say, you have a way with words, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝刀未老
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still got it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好约会了吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready for your date, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,约会的事情我都胸有成竹  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm always ready when it comes to dating, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.00,0:15:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,口气清新剂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breath spray?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.95,0:15:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸运手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lucky hanky?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.77,0:15:49.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:49.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生锈大锚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Giant rusty anchor?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.88,0:15:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anchor
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有锚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anchor?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找不到生锈大锚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't find me giant rusty anchor
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放轻松  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Relax, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一小玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a little joke
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你跟那个谁好运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck with you-know-who
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.69,0:16:03.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个谁是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:03.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.57,0:16:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.90,0:16:05.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:05.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就祝我好运吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, wish me luck, lad
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:11.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,228)}奢华
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这晚餐可真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This dinner has been so wonderful
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.68,0:16:17.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊瑚煮得恰到好处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:17.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The coral was cooked to perfection
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.24,0:16:20.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不舍得再咬一口了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:20.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think I could eat another bite
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可不见得  我的小捕虾船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I doubt that, my little shrimp boat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你太宠我了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're spoiling me, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.95,0:16:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有用餐间隙的足部按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,foot rubs between courses
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Caricatures
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有进口的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imported music
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了你一切都好得不得了  小桃桃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing's too good for you, my prickly peach
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.56,0:16:47.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我想告诉你的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:47.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I'm trying to tell you, Mr. Krabs is
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  你的豪华轿车到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, your fancy pantsy limousine is here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.22,0:16:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wonderful
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.46,0:16:54.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙小可爱  你的车在等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:54.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Puffily-poo, your chariot awaits
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你以后再也不用走路了  小围兜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never have to walk again, my little lobster bib
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.49,0:17:03.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:03.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您的账单  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your bill, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,160)}账单
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一百块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One hundred dollars
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意肯定是写错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this can't possibly be correct
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My mistake, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢您指正
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for pointing that out
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是您的账单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your bill
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不太明白了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.68,0:17:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是怎么做到一夜花十万的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can you spend $100,000 in one night?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.61,0:17:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是忍不住要把钱全花她身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but spend every cent I had on her
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是控制不住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't control myself
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.84,0:17:37.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:37.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.34,0:17:41.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明天还有一场约会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:41.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got another date tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.28,0:17:44.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夹在两个爱人之间害得我进退两难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:44.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm caught in the middle of me two great loves
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.30,0:17:48.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱的泡芙老师  还有我剩下的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:48.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sweet Mrs. Puff and the rest of me money
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望我能有什么办法帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish there was some way l could help
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能还真有办法  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps there is, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要让你来负责管理我的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm putting you in charge of me money
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不太明白  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟着我来约会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You come with me on the date
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.40,0:18:07.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我不要花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:07.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and don't let me spend any money
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记好了  去公园可以便宜点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now remember, we keep it cheap by going to the park
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且不管我向你要多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no matter how much I ask you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不能把我钱给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you don't give me any of me money
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.90,0:18:16.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:16.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now give me a dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.69,0:18:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good boy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll do fine
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.68,0:18:25.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  我可爱的小浮标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:25.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me, my beautiful bell buoy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买花啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flowers, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.11,0:18:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快买花去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.88,0:18:31.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:31.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you said
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.39,0:18:35.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能空手见泡芙老师这样的时髦淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can't call on a classy lady
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like Mrs. Puff empty-handed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱讲的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We ain't talking about this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.75,0:18:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱讲的是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're talking about this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多要好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost ready
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧的  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去买花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get the flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是一如既往地漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're as beautiful as ever
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's funny
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.49,0:18:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为我听到海绵宝宝说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I heard SpongeBob's voice
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.27,0:18:52.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:52.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.99,0:18:54.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他马上就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:54.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll be right back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.09,0:18:56.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天他是我们的私人助理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:56.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's our personal assistant for the day
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得给我保险代理人打下电话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l have to call my insurance agent
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然可以了  我美丽的泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, my beautiful Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.37,0:19:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我买了你要我买的花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the flowers you wanted me to buy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.66,0:19:10.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:10.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给泡芙老师买了花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the flowers for Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经说好了的  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We had an agreement, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不应该把我钱给花掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ain't supposed to spend any of me money
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.92,0:19:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you said
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I come
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.44,0:19:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你的  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For you, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真贴心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How thoughtful
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.29,0:19:28.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还有盒巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:28.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here's a box of chocolates
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  巧克力在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, where's the chocolates?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  预算不够买
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, the budget doesn't allow for
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  到泡芙老师家门口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you can't go to Mrs. Puff's house
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一定得有巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without chocolates
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.39,0:19:39.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去  快去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:39.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,340)}巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.33,0:19:41.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把他们店里最大盒的买了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:41.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bought the biggest box they had
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买买买
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buy, buy, buy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花花花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spend, spend, spend
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只会想到这点东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that all you can think about?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.54,0:19:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我给你买的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's those chocolates I bought for you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天我们要干什么  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are we doing today, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.43,0:19:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dinner?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dancing?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.81,0:19:55.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是去月球旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:55.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A trip to the moon?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.25,0:19:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱就只是去公园散步  记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're just going for a walk in the park, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实在公园散个步就挺好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, a walk in the park sounds perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天天气不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful day
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只要戴个遮阳帽就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'll just need to get a sun hat and
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师要遮阳帽  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff needs a sun hat, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.41,0:20:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她好像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think she
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太阳都晒到可怜的泡芙老师的头上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sun is beating down on poor Mrs. Puff's head
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作为你的财务顾问  我建议
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As your financial advisor, l suggest
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.23,0:20:14.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没时间建议了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:14.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's not time for suggestions
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.22,0:20:15.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去买帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:15.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go buy a hat
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.31,0:20:15.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:15.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别担心  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会给你遮阳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll shade you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.65,0:20:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遮阳帽来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One shady hat
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.90,0:20:23.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做得好  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:23.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good job, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.11,0:20:29.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你真的没必要买
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:29.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you didn't need to buy one
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我衣柜里已经有一顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a hat in the closet
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.84,0:20:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没必要买
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't need to buy one
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.37,0:20:35.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:35.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hear that, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没必要买帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We didn't need to buy a hat
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是该帮我省钱的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed to be saving me money?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽力了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.67,0:20:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你一直在要我给泡芙老师买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you keep telling me to buy things for Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我整个都懵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all really confusing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.32,0:20:52.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:52.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my fault
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.28,0:20:53.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不太理智了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:53.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not thinking clearly
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就此作出承诺  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm making a sailor's promise, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从现在起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From this moment on
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.13,0:21:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会再叫你给泡芙老师买任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't ask you to buy anything for Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.36,0:21:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,过了一会儿
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.67,0:21:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  泡芙老师需要新的毛大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, Mrs. Puff needs a new fur coat
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都要把我钱花光了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're spending all me money
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.41,0:21:12.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙芙需要双新鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:12.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Puffy needs a new pair of shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.58,0:21:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要把我搞破产了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're breaking me, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她需要上品珠宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She needs fine jewelry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要这么上品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not that fine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.04,0:21:33.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:33.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你能来可真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I'm glad I caught you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你给泡芙老师买
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to buy Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.61,0:21:39.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:39.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先来猜下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.37,0:21:43.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要我跑去店里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:43.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want me to run down to the store
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.69,0:21:46.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买泡芙老师根本就不需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:46.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and buy Mrs. Puff something she doesn't need
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.69,0:21:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你要我再跑回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you want me to run back here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样你就能说  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you can say, "Aye, SpongeBob"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.27,0:21:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要把我钱都花光了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're spending all me money"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.04,0:21:54.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我就说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:54.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then I'll say
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.24,0:21:57.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板  我只是在照你说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:57.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"But Mr. Krabs, I'm only doing what you said"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.39,0:21:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你就说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you'll say
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱讲的不是这个  也不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"We're not talking about this or this
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.91,0:22:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱讲的是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're talking about this"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.21,0:22:07.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是小子  这回不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:07.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But lad, this time's different
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.16,0:22:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师需要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff needs this
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还去不去公园了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are we going to the park soon?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托了小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, lad?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.07,0:22:15.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:15.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.33,0:22:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是只找到真爱的寂寞老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a lonely old crustacean who's found love
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.10,0:22:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别让我把她失去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let me lose her
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.86,0:22:23.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:23.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, don't
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.33,0:22:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.29,0:22:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.65,0:22:28.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  我马上去买总行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:28.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to get it, see?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.96,0:22:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打起精神来  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要的洗衣机来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's that washing machine you wanted
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.16,0:22:34.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:34.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheer up?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.45,0:22:36.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要怎么打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:36.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can I cheer up
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.15,0:22:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是要花光我辛辛苦苦赚的钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you're spending all me hard-earned cash?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.17,0:22:39.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:39.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.58,0:22:40.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:40.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just did it again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.83,0:22:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你乱花别人钱  我就忍不住要说你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:42.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lad, I can't help it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you're loose with other people's money
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该再给泡芙买烘干机配洗衣机用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think Mrs. Puff will need a dryer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to go along with that?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.84,0:22:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想知道我在想什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do you want to know what I think?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.73,0:22:58.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:22:58.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.40,0:23:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wallet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,862)}词典
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.86,0:23:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乱花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spend
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.15,0:23:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板的钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs' wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.82,0:23:15.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道海绵宝宝词汇量这么丰富
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:15.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't know SpongeBob had such a colorful vocabulary
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.87,0:23:19.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我也有话要说  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:19.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's something I'd like to say, too, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕我收这么多礼物会觉得不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:23.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I just don't feel comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:25.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,accepting all these gifts
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.64,0:23:27.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是各付各的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.64,0:23:27.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd rather go dutch
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.34,0:23:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.88,0:23:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.76,0:23:34.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真是可爱  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.76,0:23:34.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a very sweet man, Mr. Krabs
